{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "Il faut commencer par dire", "start": 0.083, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "la gravit\u00e9 de cet acte,", "start": 1.883, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "qui consiste \u00e0 lancer une gr\u00e8ve", "start": 3.083, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "avant d'avoir ouvert des n\u00e9gociations.", "start": 4.616, "duration": 2.3}, {"text": "Je pense qu'aujourd'hui,", "start": 6.916, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "tous les Fran\u00e7ais constatent", "start": 8.033, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "l'irresponsabilit\u00e9 de la CGT qui,", "start": 9.016, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "alors m\u00eame que les discussions", "start": 11.266, "duration": 1.15}, {"text": "n'ont pas commenc\u00e9,", "start": 12.416, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "d\u00e9cide de faire une gr\u00e8ve pr\u00e9ventive.", "start": 13.283, "duration": 1.483}, {"text": "C'est l\u00e0 une mani\u00e8re", "start": 14.766, "duration": 1.517}, {"text": "de p\u00e9naliser tous les Fran\u00e7ais,", "start": 16.283, "duration": 1.683}, {"text": "de mettre en difficult\u00e9", "start": 17.966, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "notre pays, dans un moment", "start": 18.8, "duration": 0.816}, {"text": "pourtant critique,", "start": 19.616, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "alors que la discussion", "start": 20.683, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "est aujourd'hui", "start": 22.216, "duration": 0.884}, {"text": "sur le point de s'ouvrir.", "start": 23.1, "duration": 1.583}, {"text": "Une gr\u00e8ve, \u00e7a ne sert pas \u00e0 \u00e7a.", "start": 24.683, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "Une gr\u00e8ve, \u00e7a sert \u00e0, quand on a \u00e9puis\u00e9", "start": 26.216, "duration": 2.867}, {"text": "toutes les mesures de discussion,", "start": 29.083, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "\u00e0 t\u00e9moigner de son opposition.", "start": 30.833, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "Mais l\u00e0, on n'est pas du tout", "start": 32.066, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "dans ce cas de figure.", "start": 32.783, "duration": 0.45}, {"text": "- Ce que dit la CGT, c'est : Total", "start": 33.233, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "vient de distribuer", "start": 35.333, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "2,6 milliards\u00a0d'euros", "start": 35.866, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "\u00e0 ses actionnaires,", "start": 37.066, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "on en veut une petite partie.", "start": 37.783, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "- Mais que la n\u00e9gociation ait lieu,", "start": 39.166, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "c'est n\u00e9cessaire, bien s\u00fbr.", "start": 40.816, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "\u00c9videmment,", "start": 41.783, "duration": 0.35}, {"text": "il faut discuter des salaires,", "start": 42.133, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "il faut discuter de l'ajustement salarial.", "start": 43.5, "duration": 2.066}, {"text": "Dans une p\u00e9riode d'inflation,", "start": 45.566, "duration": 1.367}, {"text": "\u00e7a peut \u00eatre parfaitement l\u00e9gitime.", "start": 46.933, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "Mais encore une fois, m\u00eame la CFDT", "start": 48.833, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "s'insurge contre ce processus,", "start": 50.966, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "cette proc\u00e9dure.", "start": 53.1, "duration": 1.016}, {"text": "Je pense que l\u00e0,", "start": 54.116, "duration": 0.467}, {"text": "il faut faire preuve", "start": 54.583, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "d'une ligne de fermet\u00e9 tr\u00e8s claire avec", "start": 55.816, "duration": 3.267}, {"text": "la CGT, en disant", "start": 59.083, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "que ce n'est pas comme \u00e7a", "start": 59.883, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "qu'on se comporte dans une d\u00e9mocratie.", "start": 60.583, "duration": 1.633}, {"text": "C'est pas en prenant", "start": 62.216, "duration": 0.617}, {"text": "en otage les Fran\u00e7ais,", "start": 62.833, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "quand la discussion,", "start": 63.916, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "encore une fois, n'a", "start": 64.583, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "m\u00eame pas encore commenc\u00e9.", "start": 65.083, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "- Une fois qu'on a d\u00e9nonc\u00e9", "start": 66.983, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "le droit de gr\u00e8ve de la CGT", "start": 67.733, "duration": 1.833}, {"text": "en ce moment, qu'est-ce", "start": 69.566, "duration": 0.65}, {"text": "qu'on fait pour", "start": 70.216, "duration": 1.0}, {"text": "amener du carburant dans les stations ?", "start": 71.233, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "- Il fallait effectivement mobiliser", "start": 74.183, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "les stocks strat\u00e9giques.", "start": 75.733, "duration": 1.167}, {"text": "Heureusement, cela a \u00e9t\u00e9 fait.", "start": 76.9, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "Le gouvernement dit que, maintenant,", "start": 78.066, "duration": 1.7}, {"text": "la situation va s'am\u00e9liorer.", "start": 79.766, "duration": 1.217}, {"text": "Et j'esp\u00e8re", "start": 80.983, "duration": 0.333}, {"text": "qu'elle s'am\u00e9liorera tr\u00e8s vite,", "start": 81.316, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "parce qu'aujourd'hui, c'est", "start": 82.25, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "des dizaines de milliers de Fran\u00e7ais", "start": 82.916, "duration": 1.467}, {"text": "qui sont p\u00e9nalis\u00e9s,", "start": 84.383, "duration": 1.017}, {"text": "qui ne peuvent pas aller travailler,", "start": 85.4, "duration": 0.983}, {"text": "qui ne peuvent pas", "start": 86.383, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "vivre leur vie normalement", "start": 87.733, "duration": 1.333}, {"text": "\u00e0 cause de cette situation.", "start": 89.066, "duration": 1.4}, {"text": "Et donc ces stocks strat\u00e9giques,", "start": 90.466, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "il fallait les d\u00e9bloquer.", "start": 91.766, "duration": 1.217}, {"text": "Heureusement, c'est", "start": 92.983, "duration": 0.633}, {"text": "une r\u00e9alit\u00e9 aujourd'hui.", "start": 93.616, "duration": 1.717}, {"text": "- Est-ce qu'il", "start": 95.333, "duration": 0.083}, {"text": "faut d\u00e9bloquer aussi les raffineries ?", "start": 95.416, "duration": 2.267}, {"text": "- Je crois qu'aujourd'hui,", "start": 97.683, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "le probl\u00e8me est plut\u00f4t", "start": 99.583, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "la question de l'acheminement", "start": 100.433, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "que la question du blocage.", "start": 101.233, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "Le probl\u00e8me,", "start": 102.133, "duration": 0.267}, {"text": "il est \u00e0 la fois dans les raffineries", "start": 102.4, "duration": 1.716}, {"text": "qui n'envoie plus de...", "start": 104.116, "duration": 0.9}, {"text": "- Mais le probl\u00e8me, c'est", "start": 105.016, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "que si vous n'avez pas de camions,", "start": 105.683, "duration": 1.433}, {"text": "\u00e7a pose un autre probl\u00e8me.", "start": 107.116, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "\u00c7a pose aussi la question,", "start": 107.966, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "encore une fois,", "start": 108.816, "duration": 0.834}, {"text": "de l'organisation de l'emploi", "start": 109.65, "duration": 1.183}, {"text": "dans le pays.", "start": 110.833, "duration": 0.4}, {"text": "Mais aujourd'hui,", "start": 111.233, "duration": 0.417}, {"text": "on manque de chauffeurs", "start": 111.65, "duration": 0.833}, {"text": "de poids lourds,", "start": 112.483, "duration": 0.433}, {"text": "on manque de chauffeur de camion,", "start": 112.916, "duration": 1.284}, {"text": "pour transporter le p\u00e9trole.", "start": 114.2, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "Donc la question c'est aussi celle-l\u00e0.", "start": 115.733, "duration": 1.717}]}